                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">News</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Commission Holds Environmental Summit in Chisinau</li>
            </ol>
        </nav>

        <div class="row g-4">

            <!-- ARTICLE -->
            <article class="col-lg-8">

                <!-- Title + meta -->
                <header class="mb-3">
                    <h1 class="fw-bold mb-2">Commission Holds Environmental Summit in Chisinau</h1>

                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center gap-2 text-muted small">
                        <span><i class="bi bi-calendar3 me-1"></i> 26 November 2025</span>
                        <span class="d-none d-sm-inline">•</span>
                        <span><i class="bi bi-tag me-1"></i> News</span>
                        <span class="d-none d-sm-inline">•</span>
                        <span><i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-1"></i> Chisinau</span>
                        <span class="d-none d-sm-inline">•</span>
                        <span><i class="bi bi-clock me-1"></i> 6 min read</span>
                    </div>
                </header>

                <!-- Featured image -->
                <figure class="mb-4">
                    <img src="images/slide1.png" class="img-fluid w-100" alt="Environmental Summit in Chisinau">
                    <figcaption class="text-muted small mt-2">
                        Delegations discussed monitoring approaches and cross-border cooperation on the Dniester River.
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>

                <!-- Lead / summary -->
                <div class="p-3 p-md-4 mb-4" style="background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        Experts and representatives of the Parties met in Chisinau to review progress on water management,
                        discuss new monitoring approaches, and coordinate upcoming joint activities and projects.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Article body -->
                <div class="content-article">

                    <p>
                        The meeting focused on the Commission’s current priorities and the upcoming work programme. Participants
                        exchanged updates on monitoring results, data interoperability, and reporting formats, with particular
                        attention to improving the accessibility of public information.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mt-4">Key outcomes</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Agreement on the next steps for harmonising monitoring indicators and reporting cycles.</li>
                        <li>Preliminary alignment on data exchange requirements for GIS/HIS modules.</li>
                        <li>Planning of joint field visits and capacity-building activities for 2026.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mt-4">Background</h2>
                    <p>
                        The Dniester River Basin requires coordinated action among riparian stakeholders. The Commission supports
                        cooperation through shared monitoring, joint initiatives, and dissemination of official information,
                        publications, and public awareness materials.
                    </p>

                    <blockquote class="p-3 my-4" style="background: var(--bg-secondary); border-left: 4px solid #007bc5;">
                        <p class="mb-1">
                            “The Commission’s work depends on consistent data and transparent communication. This meeting helps
                            us advance both.”
                        </p>
                        <footer class="small text-muted">— Statement for demonstration purposes</footer>
                    </blockquote>

                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mt-4">Documents</h2>
                    <div class="list-group mb-4">
                        <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <span><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text me-2"></i> Meeting agenda (PDF)</span>
                            <span class="badge text-bg-secondary">PDF</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <span><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-arrow-down me-2"></i> Summary conclusions (PDF)</span>
                            <span class="badge text-bg-secondary">PDF</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <span><i class="bi bi-link-45deg me-2"></i> Related project page</span>
                            <span class="badge text-bg-secondary">Link</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mt-4">Tags</h2>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
                        <a href="#" class="badge text-bg-secondary text-decoration-none">Monitoring</a>
                        <a href="#" class="badge text-bg-secondary text-decoration-none">Water Management</a>
                        <a href="#" class="badge text-bg-secondary text-decoration-none">Cooperation</a>
                        <a href="#" class="badge text-bg-secondary text-decoration-none">Chisinau</a>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <!-- Article footer: share + back -->
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between align-items-center gap-3 mt-4 pt-3"
                     style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="text-muted small">Share:</span>
                        <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i></a>
